  OrderIdx: 3
  Title: "H\xC0NH TR\xCCNH H\u1ECCC THU\u1EACT "
  HexCode: 0x190A
  Content:
  - "Ngay trong kh\xF3a tuy\u1EC3n sinh \u0111\u1EA7u ti\xEAn n\u0103m 2006, UIT
    \u0111\xE3 m\u1EDF ng\xE0nh \u201C________ M\xE1y t\xEDnh\u201D \u2014 l\u0129nh
    v\u1EF1c nghi\xEAn c\u1EE9u n\u1EC1n t\u1EA3ng v\u1EC1 thu\u1EADt to\xE1n, tr\xED
    tu\u1EC7 nh\xE2n t\u1EA1o v\xE0 t\u01B0 duy t\xEDnh to\xE1n c\u1ED1t l\xF5i c\u1EE7a
    ng\xE0nh CNTT."
  - "Ng\xE0nh ____ xu\u1EA5t hi\u1EC7n t\u1EEB nh\u1EEFng n\u0103m \u0111\u1EA7u
    th\xE0nh l\u1EADp UIT, chuy\xEAn \u0111\xE0o t\u1EA1o v\u1EC1 h\u1EA1 t\u1EA7ng
    Internet, h\u1EC7 th\u1ED1ng truy\u1EC1n d\u1EEF li\u1EC7u, giao th\u1EE9c k\u1EBFt
    n\u1ED1i v\xE0 v\u1EADn h\xE0nh m\u1EA1ng quy m\xF4 l\u1EDBn."
  - "T\u1EF7 l\u1EC7 sinh vi\xEAn UIT c\xF3 vi\u1EC7c l\xE0m sau t\u1ED1t nghi\u1EC7p
    lu\xF4n n\u1EB1m trong nh\xF3m cao c\u1EE7a c\u1EA3 n\u01B0\u1EDBc. \u0110\u1EB1ng
    sau con s\u1ED1 \u1EA5y l\xE0 h\xE0nh tr\xECnh 20 ________ li\xEAn t\u1EE5c \u0111\u1ED5i
    m\u1EDBi ch\u01B0\u01A1ng tr\xECnh \u0111\xE0o t\u1EA1o, c\u1EADp nh\u1EADt c\xF4ng
    ngh\u1EC7 v\xE0 k\u1EBFt n\u1ED1i doanh nghi\u1EC7p."
